data.description: Welcome to this charming 3-bed, 2-bath, 1460 sqft home with volume ceilings and a thoughtful layout. Interior features include a blend of tile w/ carpet flooring. The kitchen boasts dark wood cabinets, and recent upgrades include a new disposal and 1 yr old refrigerator, washer, and dryer. Roll-up electrical shades provide convenience on the patio sliders and all back-facing windows. The home offers a walk-in closet, pantry, and split bedroom layout. Enjoy pond views from your backyard with the extended covered lanai, adding tranquility. The eat-in kitchen and bar area offer versatile spaces for dining and entertaining. This community includes an unmanned gate & playground and has no pet restrictions. Discover the potential of this well-maintained property.  Call today for a private tour!
